channel.title: Your account is already logged in
channel.description: Ok first off, I don't know if this belongs in the client help section, or the server help section. Second, on my client, when I try to log in to my server, after it loads I try to log on to my server and this shows up [IMG]http://i707.photobucket.com/albums/ww76/Jakesta96/glitch2.jpg[/img] and in my run.bat for my server, this shows up Connection from 0:0:0:0:0:0:0:1:56892 [client-1-Jake]: Loading Process Completed [Has powers, lag: 51 ms] ClientHandler: Client null disconnected (0:0:0:0:0:0:0:1) although this only happens on my first attempt of logging in when I start up my client, if I try a 2nd time it lets me log in. What do I do to make this stop?
